               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I intended to replace the money—Mr. Dobson re<lb></lb>ceived 30<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. of the amount of my father, and said if that money was replaced, he did not wish to press the charge.</p>
